  <brief_title>Burn Scar Appearance After Treatment With Fractional Carbon Dioxide (CO2) Laser</brief_title>
  <official_title>Burn Scar Characteristics After Treatment With Fractional CO2 Laser: A Clinical and Histological Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
